Dear all,

The professor position we had last spring in Chambery has not been
taken, and should be reopened in the next few weeks.
The new professor will join the LIMD group

http://www.lama.univ-savoie.fr/index1.php?use=membres&equipe=logique&lang=en

and teach at the math department of University of Savoy.

Categorists are particularly welcome to apply, as a few of us use
categories in their research, and category theory is a theme we are
willing to develop in the future.

Applications should be next spring, but there is a mandatory
'qualification' procedure starting soon.
So please don't hesitate to contact us quickly if you are interested,
or for any question or suggestion you might have.

Pierre Hyvernat and Tom Hirschowitz




